  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK222">
<l>nallā ṟeṉiṉuṅ koḷaṟītu mēlulaka</l>
<l>milleṉiṉu mītalē naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To beg is evil, even though it were said that it is a good path (to heaven). To give is good, even though it were said that those who do so cannot obtain heaven.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
